8:38 a.m. Sept. 15, 2016
					  - By Lawrence G. McMillan
		  
The picture has turned somewhat bearish with the SPX breaking support, and as a result, we are changing our stance to “sell on rallies.” If the support at 2120 were clearly to be broken, an even more aggressive bearish stance would be warranted.


