                                         options and will probably eventually come to be known as the “SPX VIX.”  You may already know that the CBOE has been publishing a VIX calculation on several stocks and commodities for some time. For example, there is an “Oil VIX” 

                            
                            
                                  
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
                                  
